            specifications</head>
          <desc type="definition" xml:lang="en">The equipment specifications of the instrument and
            the overall appartus are documented such as type of equipment, manufacturing company,
            laser excitation wavelength, optical system (camera) /objective lens used and any other
            component used.<list>
              <item>Possible source of error: If possible a proper excitation line should me used
                for spefic materials. Both in consideration of stability under the laser, the
                scattering probability and also photochemical damage should be considered.</item>
            </list></desc>
